       Make a linked list of radiobutton nodes from the @{"NULL" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 101} terminated
       label array. The labels are not copied, so they must stay
       valid until the list is free'd.@{b}

   INPUTS@{ub}
       array -- a @{"NULL" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 101} terminated array of string pointers.@{b}

   RESULTS@{ub}
       list -- a linked list of radiobutton nodes

@ENDNODE
